wikipedia_page.main: Charlotte Green (born (1994-05-16)16 May 1994) is an English female  BMX rider, from Threemilestone, near Truro, Cornwall. She has represented Great Britain at international competitions. She competed in the time trial event and race event at the 2015 UCI BMX World Championships.
